---
title: Roasted Pork Loin with Sweet Potato Mash and Creamy Peppercorn Sauce
description: We’ve taken the best pork loin we could lay our hands on and teamed it up with super nutritious sweet potato mash. With our favourite peppercorn sauce, this quick weeknight meal could easily pass for a weekend specialty.
